                                                                                                 4 Definitions

                                                                                                 This list of Acronyms and the glossary of terms contains elements that are not already defined by the
                                                                                                 CC or CEM:
                                                                                                 AES                  Advanced Encryption Standard
                                                                                                 CBC                  Cipher Block Chaining (a block cipher mode of operation)
